title: Online share of retail trade in selected countries 2014 to 2018
summary: This grouped bar chart represents 12 different Countrys on X-axis for 5 groups 2014, 2015, 2016, 2017, and 2018. On the Y-axis it shows their corresponding SOME LABEL.
Country United Kingdom had the maximum SOME LABEL among all 5 groups, and it was for 2017. The minimum SOME LABEL was observed in Country Switzerland for 2014.
Among all the Countrys, 2018 had the highest SOME LABEL 178.0 in Country United Kingdom and lowest value 34.0 in Country Italy.
There is a gap of 144.0 between the highest and lowest SOME LABEL found for 2018 in Country United Kingdom and Italy.
